{
  "stem": "3721.3",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And when I asked him, what's happening in our hometown, he says, well, you know, I was there when our-- your-- our hometown was liberated the first day.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "But they were liberated by the Czech army, not by the Russians.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "So I was-- just sort of went through.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I was there a half a day.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And at that time, everything looked as normal as, as could be.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "The only thing is-- without Jews.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Couldn't believe it, he says.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "There's nobody there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And he told me of one individual that survived, who was also hiding between two buildings, and survived the war because he had outside help.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "You see, we didn't have outside help.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "That was one of our mistakes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "However, I don't know, in our case, how the outside help would have worked.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "In his case, the neighbor was the one.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "They were between two buildings.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "There was a, a building area.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And he was there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And they supplied him with food and water.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "I don't know how they could have done it in my case.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "Because in my case, the German headquarters were above us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So anyway, I survived, and so did the other people survive-- also in a Schutz House, I don't know whether the Swedish one or the Swiss one.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then, two or three days, I told you before, I started going home in a overnight train that was going back to Russia to pick up-- pick up-- I don't know, whatever.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was an empty train.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was terribly, terribly cold.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was an awfully cold winter.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was clothed very lightly.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I was in this freight wagon all by myself, with a little straw on it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I covered myself with straw.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then we got into one of the cities.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
